:INFO
Weekly Body Doubling Schedule
A repeating schedule reduces the friction of starting. Block these sessions in your calendar as recurring commitments, not optional suggestions.

:TASK
[ ] Monday 9am: Morning deep work session (90 min, Focusmate)
[ ] Tuesday 2pm: Admin and email catch-up (45 min, Discord partner)
[ ] Wednesday 9am: Writing or creative work (90 min, Focusmate)
[ ] Thursday 2pm: Review and planning session (45 min, solo or partner)
[ ] Friday 10am: Weekly wrap-up and next week prep (60 min)
[ ] Weekend optional: Open coworking session for personal projects

:NOTE
Treat cancellations as reschedules, not failures. If a partner cancels, use ambient coworking YouTube streams or a cafe recording as a substitute.
